{"tid":954102,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"警方觀塘工業區掃黃　拘十四名內地女","createTime":"2018-12-24T11:28:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T14:58:05.000Z","uid":99861,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e53a4560e6cf04ee02ba1c9babbedff58e793940","tid":954102,"uid":99861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T11:28:48.000Z","msg":"觀塘警區特別職務隊、觀塘警區特遣隊、秀茂坪警區特別職務隊及入境事務處人員，今日（6日）上午約9時展開代號「萬里達」(MILESMETER) 及「孤影」(LONESHADOW)的掃黃行動，在康寧道、輔仁街、崇仁街、<span style=\"color: red;\">瑞和街</span>、宜安街及觀塘工業區一帶拘捕14名年齡介乎25至45歲持雙程證的內地女子，涉嫌「違反逗留條件」。所有被捕女子現正被扣留調查，稍後將交入境事務處跟進。"},{"pid":"08990b6b03e1debc43746e764592a9c50e73be36","tid":954102,"uid":170504,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T11:31:57.000Z","msg":"終於掃走班嘔心阿婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c49f2414914a494c6de09bf5b368c630407e63","tid":954102,"uid":99861,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"08990b6b03e1debc43746e764592a9c50e73be36","tid":954102,"uid":170504,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T11:31:57.000Z","msg":"終於掃走班嘔心阿婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T11:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c691d8229a59e1fea65524256d0e24a38b72da0","tid":954102,"uid":47005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08990b6b03e1debc43746e764592a9c50e73be36","tid":954102,"uid":170504,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T11:31:57.000Z","msg":"終於掃走班嘔心阿婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=